                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-403-18610408 t18610408-403-punishment-112"></join>Confined Four Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">ADJOURNED TO MONDAY, MAY</hi> 6<hi rend="smallCaps">TH</hi>, 1861.</p>
